cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you reference this work, please cite as below."
title: "Lodestar / IgniteAI: An HBCU Student Career-Advice Chatbot"
abstract: >
  Reference implementation and preservation of IgniteAI, a career-advice
  chatbot for students at Historically Black Colleges and Universities (HBCUs).
  Originally built as a ChatGPT custom GPT by Team 4 of the HP Future of Work
  Accelerator (FOWA) 2024 at the HBCU Technology Conference, where it won first
  place. This repository preserves the shipped custom-GPT product and provides
  a clean, runnable Python reference implementation (OpenAI gpt-4o-mini grounded
  on an academic/career/internship knowledge base) that mirrors its behavior.
type: software
